synopsis.text: Race through the cosmos with the unconventional 108th prince of the Galactic Empire, Muscat Tyler, in a thrilling anime adventure! Joined by his loyal companions, the formidable walking armory K.K. and the unparalleled powerhouse Ruu of the Lightwing race, this eccentric trio explores the far reaches of the universe. But be prepared for chaos, as their interstellar journey consistently attracts trouble at every turn!
